## Data Flow Summary

```
HEAD assigns items → ONE task created in tasks_tbl
                       ↓ task_items_tbl (junction)
                     app_item_id_fk → app_items_tbl
                                         ↓
                                      app_id_fk → app_tbl

app_items_tbl.app_items_assigned_to:
  NULL    = not yet assigned
  user_id = assigned to this user
```

